# A380 flyPad/MCDU live Coherent debugging tools are now TRACKED — they're the
# primary way to read/write L:vars and scrape the cockpit DOM against the running
# sim, and genuinely useful to co-developers. See tools/_probe/README.md and the
# header of tools/coherent-eval.ps1.

# Local-only ECAM port workspace (downloaded FBW source + generators); ships as MSFSBlindAssist/SimConnect/EWDMessageLookupA380.cs
tools/_fbw_ecam/
# jsdom test deps for the flyPad shell reconcile (Gus A32NX)
tools/flypad-shell-test/node_modules/
# jsdom test deps for the flyPad Settings/doors scrape regression harness
tools/flypad-settings-test/node_modules/
tools/_probe/engmon/
tools/_probe/engmon_ctrle/

# Global: stray npm trees anywhere (a root-level jsdom tree once slipped into a commit)
node_modules/

# OSM census/audit collector artifacts (not part of the augmentation feature)
tools/osm-audit/
